    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Sonic Thrust</strong><span style=\"font-weight:normal\"> (</span><span class=\"t_nihongo_kanji\" lang=\"ja\">瞬迅剣</span> <span class=\"t_nihongo_romaji\"><em>Shunjinken</em></span>, \"Instantaneous Rapid Sword\"), alternatively <strong>Sonic Dog</strong><span style=\"font-weight:normal\"> (</span><span class=\"t_nihongo_kanji\" lang=\"ja\">瞬迅犬</span> <span class=\"t_nihongo_romaji\"><em>Shunjinken</em></span>, \"Instantaneous Rapid Dog\") and <strong>Flying Jab</strong><span style=\"font-weight:normal\"> (</span><span class=\"t_nihongo_kanji\" lang=\"ja\">瞬迅拳</span> <span class=\"t_nihongo_romaji\"><em>Shunjinken</em></span>, \"Instantaneous Rapid Fist\"), is a classic sword technique where the user of the arte dashes forward and executes a powerful stab, empowered by wind and sound.</p><p>You Step, and you make a Strike with a melee attack at the end of your movement. Your Strike gains the Air and Versatile Sonic trait.</p><p>If you spend a focus point when you use this action, you can instead perform a Stride with a +10-foot circumstance bonus to your Speed.</p>"
